WEBVTT

00:05:29.208 --> 00:05:31.268
even when she's being exploited.

00:05:31.292 --> 00:05:34.018
Amisha, who is 18, said,

00:05:34.042 --> 00:05:36.309
"My father said,

00:05:36.333 --> 00:05:39.333
'If I don't see you smiling,
I don't feel good.'"

00:05:40.167 --> 00:05:41.476
So she smiles.

00:05:41.500 --> 00:05:44.059
So her father is teaching her,

00:05:44.083 --> 00:05:48.018
my happiness is more important
than your happiness.

00:05:48.042 --> 00:05:52.268
And in this business of trying
to make everyone happy all the time,

00:05:52.292 --> 00:05:55.167
girls become afraid to make decisions.

00:05:56.042 --> 00:05:58.643
And when you ask them, they say,

00:05:58.667 --> 00:06:01.042
"Anything, whatever! Kuch bhi!